-1 |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Orwell |first=George |author-link = George Orwell |year=2000 |orig-year = 1938 |title = Homage to Catalonia |publisher=Penguin, Martin Secker & Warburg |location=Londo, England n |isbn=0-14-118305-5 |oclc = 42954349 |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last= Othen |first=Christopher |year=2008 |title = Franco's International Brigades: Foreign Volunteers and Fascist Dictators in the Spanish Civil War |publisher=Reportage Press |location = London, England |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last= Payne |first= Stanley G. |url= http://www.cambridge.org/us/academic/subjects/history/twentieth-century-european-history/spanish-civil-war |title=The Spanish Civil War |year=2012 |isbn = 978-0-521-17470-1 | publisher = Cambridge University Press |ref = harv}}\n* {{Cite book |last = Payne |first = Stanley G. |year = 2004 |title = The Spanish Civil War, the Soviet Union, and Communism |publisher = Yale University Press |location = New Haven, CT; London, England |isbn = 0-300-10068-X |oclc = 186010979 |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last = Payne |first = Stanley G. |chapter-url = http://libro.uca.edu/payne2/payne26.htm |chapter=The Spanish Civil War of 1936-1939 |title = A History of Spain and Portugal |volume = 2 |publisher= University of Wisconsin Press |year=1973 |via = Library of Iberian resources online |access-date = 15 May 2007 |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last = Payne |first = Stanley G. |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=NiD3UeOCSGsC&pg=PA200 |title = Fascism in Spain, 1923\u20131977 |year = 1999 |publisher = University of Wisconsin Press |isbn = 0-299-16564-7 |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last = Payne |first = Stanley G. |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KPgPFqXub14C |title = Franco and Hitler: Spain, Germany, and World War II |year = 2008 |location = [[New Haven, Connecticut|Connecticut]], [[Connecticut|CT]] |isbn = 978-0-300-12282-4 |publisher =Yale University Press |ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Preston |first=Paul |author-lin