1130013459/http://flag.blackened.net/revolt/spaindx.html The role of anarchism in the Spanish Revolution]\n* [http://www.spanish-civil-war-collection.com Private Collection about German Exile and Spanish Civil War]\n* ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20170825105001/http://www.archives.gov.on.ca/en/explore/online/spain/index.aspx The Archives of Ontario Remembers Children's Art from the Spanish Civil War]'', online exhibit on Archives of Ontario website\n\n{{-}}\n{{Spanish Civil War}}\n{{Nazi\u2013Soviet relations}}\n{{Spain topics|state=collapsed}}\n{{Anarchism}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Spanish Civil War| ]]\n[[Category:Carlism]]\n[[Category:Civil wars involving the states and peoples of Europe]]\n[[Category:1930s conflicts]]\n[[Category:1930s in Spain]]\n[[Category:Francoist Spain]]\n[[Category:Modern history of Spain]]\n[[Category:Wars involving Spain]]\n[[Category:Revolution-based civil wars]]\n[[Category:Proxy wars]]\n", "name_user": "I Am Cracked", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Fixed typo)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spanish_Civil_War"}
